Intallare Grafana su Kubernetes:

kubectl create -f grafana-datasource-config.yaml

kubectl create -f deployment.yaml

kubectl create -f service.yaml

kubectl get po -n monitoring

A questo punto potremo accedere a Grafana da: localhost:30001

In alternativa:

kubectl port-forward -n monitoring ***nome_pod*** 3000 &
[Per esempio: kubectl port-forward -n monitoring grafana-64c89f57f7-r7n5q 3000 &]

localhost:3000

User: admin
Password: admin
